data.description: From the moment you enter, you'll be impressed by the spaciousness and comfort of this nearly new double wide manufactured home. It's the perfect place to call ''home sweet home.'' This 3 bed 2 bath home sits on nearly 2 acres of cleared land. If its peace and quiet you want than this is the home for you. There is an electric fireplace that produces heat and has an array of light settings you can choose from to create just the right ambience. Primary bath has a large bath tub. Outside you will find a very nice dog pen, it is set up with 7 individual pens and a storage area at the end. This home is a must see. Trampoline does not convey. All information in the MSL is intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed.
